    <string name="view_question_share">Share</string>
 	<string name="about_us_description">This vision of our team is to allow everyone to seek opinions from all over the world and analyze the results based on important data points. An unbiased and unfiltered look at the opinions of the everybody on any issue can be truly eye opening.</string>
 	<string name="learn_more_descripton">- Every person in this world is unique, their perspectives can be shaped by the environment, their family, culture, religion and many other factors.</string>
 	<string name="learn_more_description2">- RaiPoll aims to represent the opinions of people in a wide range of issues from entertainment politics, sports to simple things in life.</string> 
 	<string name="learn_more_description3">- Our goal is to inform the public about attitudes and trends shaping the world. You can think of RaiPoll as combining the simplicity of a survey with focused and clear result representation for everone.</string>
 	<string name="learn_more_description4">- Join us in building this unique community and get started asking and voting about anything that interests you. All voting is kept anonymous while aggregate information is accessible to all members of the community.</string>
 	    
